headline: NVIDIA (NVDA) Servers Power India's First AI GPU Cloud From Novacore Innovations
summary: NVIDIA (NVDA) recently powered Novacore Innovations' launch of India's first GPU cloud platform, marking a significant leap in AI infrastructure. During the last quarter, NVIDIA's stock rose 33%, potentially driven by strong earnings with a net income surge and increased hardware adoption by major firms like Disney and Foxconn. These factors were pivotal amidst a tech-heavy market retreat, where major indices like the Nasdaq fell, while NVIDIA bucked the trend. The company's embrace by tech...

headline: Kayou Expands into Mature Markets with Debut at Tokyo Toy Show 2025
summary: Kayou, a leading player in China's pan-entertainment and collectibles industry, is accelerating its global expansion with a two-pronged exhibition strategy. Following its debut at the 2025 Indonesia International Baby Products & Toys Expo (IBTE Indonesia) on August 20, Kaiyou unveiled its flagship lineup at the 59th Tokyo Toy Show on August 28, reflecting its structured approach to building a global presence and scaling internationally.
